  <li id="comment-21255" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://buttersweetmelody.wordpress.com/" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">buttersweetmelody</a></cite></div>
