    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Your post on plums brought to mind the poem by William Carlos Williams &#8220;This Is Just To Say&#8221;</p>
<p>If you&#39;re not familiar with it, here it is (link below).  </p>
<p>You make food so poetic, so I just had to share this poem&#8211;in case you haven&#39;t heard it before.</p>
<p><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/This_Is_Just_To_Say" rel="nofollow ugc">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/This_Is_Just_To_Say</a></p>
