    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Angela, I do think this tart would freeze nicely.  You might lose some of the crispy texture around the edges &#8211; winding up, then, with a more uniformly cakey / chewy result &#8211; but I don&#39;t think that&#39;s a big deal.</p>
